Darrell K. Hughes



Mr. Darrell K. Hughes is Chief Executive Officer at Aurora Plastics, Inc. and President at Two Rivers Bank & Trust (Burlington, Iowa). He is on the Board of Directors at Advansix, Inc. Mr. Hughes was previously employed as Vice President & GM-Fasson Roll North America by Avery Dennison Corp. He also served on the board at Two Rivers Financial Group, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Bucknell University and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



