 Aurora Plastics Appoints New Customer Service Representative			 June 19, 2017/in Uncategorized /by de99ison



STREETSBORO, OH – June 19, 2017 – Aurora Plastics, LLC, a leader in PVC compounds, announces the appointment of Janet Martineau as customer service representative.
In her role, Janet will provide service and support to Aurora Plastics’ customers, ensuring that the company will meet its commitments.  She will also support the sales team, facilitating questions and /or requests for product information. 
Prior to joining Aurora Plastics, Janet held various customer service roles at PPG, in addition to serving as an administrator for their key distributor program, the Platinum Program.
“We are excited to have Janet on the team,” says Steve Harrigan, vice president of sales, Aurora Plastics.  “She brings the right combination of communication and sales support skills needed to meet our operating plan objectives and continue providing outstanding service to our customers which differentiates us in the industry.”
Janet holds a bachelor’s degree in psychology from Cleveland State University.  She begins her position effective immediately.
Janet can be reached by phone at (330).626.6438.


